# [RCAL] Brain tumor segmentation

End-of-course project at EPITA, major Image 2021, course RCAL

Authors:
    - Simon Regourd , simon.regourd@epita.fr
    - Stanislas Sokolov, stanislas.sokolov@epita.fr

# Usage

Use Python 3.8

There are two scripts:
    - seg.py is to segment the tumor
    - vision.py is to visualize the tumor in the Brain

To use them, create an virtual python environement, install the requirements
with pip and you are ready to go.

'''
42$ python -m venv env
42$ . env/bin/activate
42$ pip install -r requirements.txt
42$ python seg.py
42$ python vision.py
'''

For more info you can use the help option (-h) to show the usage of each script. 